  "description": "A jungle-like dimension mod!",
  "body": "<p>The Silva, a jungle-like dimension mod!</p>\n<p>Welcome to the Silva, The Silva is a old mod which I made around the same time as The 7 Realms so it's in my old style of modding where I was pretty new to it so it's not very good. The reason I wanted to upload this mod is to archive my progress with modding so that I may one day look back upon where I started.</p>\n<p>So feel free to explore this dimension in its scuffed glory. You enter the dimension by building a nether portal-like frame using the \"Superior Gold Block\" and then lighting it using \"The Forever Flame\" item.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/creraces\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3.2.0/assets/cozy/donate/patreon-singular_vector.svg\" alt=\"Donate\" width=\"186\" height=\"56\" /></a> <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/forge_vector.svg\" alt=\"Available for Forge\" width=\"186\" height=\"56\" /> <a href=\"https://discord.gg//jwAeWYyGug\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/discord-plural_vector.svg\" alt=\"Join the Discord\" width=\"186\" height=\"56\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"Join the Discord!\" href=\"https://discord.gg/QagkwvSWtC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/844129861861376042?label=Join%20the%20Discord%21&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=FFFFFF\" alt=\"https://discord.gg/QagkwvSWtC\" width=\"181\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Supported Versions:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><i><strong>1.7.10:</strong>&nbsp;N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.12.2:</strong> N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.14.4:</strong> N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.15.2:</strong> N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.16.5: </strong><em>ARC: \"Archived\"</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.17.1: </strong>N/A:&nbsp;<em>None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.18.2:</strong>&nbsp;ARC: <em>\"Archived\"</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong> 1.19.2:</strong><em> N/A:&nbsp;None</em></i></p>\n<p><i><strong>1.19.4:</strong><em> ???: ???</em></i></p>\n<p><i><em>Do note that this is the plan but things may change overtime!</em></i></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary><strong>FAQ:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>1. <b>coming soon...</b></p>\n</div>\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary><strong>Credits:</strong></summary>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><em><strong>Developers:</strong></em></p>\n<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a title=\"mc_jojo3&nbsp;\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><em>Textures:</em></strong></p>\n<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a title=\"mc_jojo3\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a> &amp; other</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Made by: <a title=\"mc_jojo3\" href=\"https://www.legacy.curseforge.com/members/mc_jojo3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mc_jojo3</a></p>",
